title: *QUARANTINE SPECIAL* I Am Talent Pt. II with Chris Black
description:
GANG BACK IN THE STU! We’re diving back in headfirst with the Throwing Fits Extended Universe’s most controversial figure, Chris Black, for the second half of our barn-burning conversation. The gd mf boyz and CB wade-knee deep into the meat and potatoes, asking the big questions only: What can Done To Death Projects do to help TF stay hot? How much money is enough for a man about town? What’s dating liked as a divorced East Coast Media Elite? Will Public Announcement ever return? All this and more thoughtfully unpacked and answered on this Patreon-exclusive episode of The Only Podcast That Matters™.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits.
